name: lo(ck/ve) story
description:
No matter how much pain has been flowed through your eyes, no matter if all are acceptable certified copies,  no matter if you have not met the person yet, the one has been part of you since the beginning. But it DOES matter to have hope, to stay strong, and to stay positive.  
One day the key will turn firmly in the lock and will open your heart through your mind.
